          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1651596469185-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> with the<strong> curried vegetables</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>golden chicken</strong> and<strong> diced tomato</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>spicy coriander chutney</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
